## Step 9 - per-camera-controller-and-status-rewrite
Done
Replaced the global stream/state in `camera-panel.js` with per-camera `CameraController` instances driven by an explicit state machine, fast direct-capture probe with `sessionStorage` transport cache, dedicated `<img>`/badge per camera, and clean open/close lifecycle (no more double-init race).
